                "invention-title": [
                    "Nickel-cobalt-based hydrotalcite-basic cobalt carbonate composite electrode material and preparation method and application thereof",
                    "镍钴基水滑石-碱式碳酸钴复合电极材料及制备方法与应用"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a nickel-cobalt-based hydrotalcite-basic cobalt hydrochloride composite electrode material and a preparation method and application thereof, and belongs to energy functional materials. The nickel foam (NF) is pretreated by hydrochloric acid, and the Ni &lt; x &gt; Co &lt; 3-x &gt; M LDH-CoHC/NF composite electrode material is prepared by a one-step solvothermal method (x represents the feeding amount of bivalent Ni metal ions; m is any one of Cr &lt; 3 + &gt;, Al &lt; 3 + &gt;, Fe &lt; 3 + &gt; and V &lt; 3 + &gt;, the total feeding molar ratio of bivalent Ni and Co metal ions to trivalent M metal ions is (Ni + Co)/M = 3/1), and the typical morphological feature is that LDH nanosheets and CoHC nanowires grow on the surface of the porous NF skeleton in a staggered manner. The obtained nickel-cobalt-based hydrotalcite-basic cobalt carbonate composite electrode material is easy to recover and reuse, shows excellent performance in urea oxidation and urea-assisted water electrolysis hydrogen production, is beneficial to solving the problems that urea pollutes the environment and the hydrogen production cost is high, and improves the practicability of a catalyst."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开一种镍钴基水滑石‑碱式盐酸钴复合电极材料及其制备方法与应用，属于能源功能材料。采用盐酸预处理泡沫镍(NF)，并通过一步溶剂热法制备NixCo3‑xM LDH‑CoHC/NF复合电极材料(x代表二价Ni金属离子的投料量；M为Cr3+、Al3+、Fe3+和V3+中的任意一种，总的二价Ni、Co金属离子和三价M金属离子投料摩尔比为(Ni+Co)/M＝3/1)，其典型的形貌特征为LDH纳米片和CoHC纳米线交错生长在多孔NF骨架表面。本发明所得镍钴基水滑石‑碱式碳酸钴复合电极材料不但易于回收和再利用，而且在尿素氧化和尿素辅助电解水制氢方面展现出优异的性能，有利于解决尿素污染环境和制氢成本高的问题，提高了催化剂的实用性。"
                }
            ]
        }
